{"tid":385650,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"多啦A夢負95歲生日！「家鄉」高岡市漫遊","createTime":"2017-09-03T11:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-03T13:00:04.000Z","uid":9573,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e7d8a37172df5e1ab3e0a0f6edeac5030ebd0736","tid":385650,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_01p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_01p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=c9cc16ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對不少動漫迷來說，明天（9月3日）是值得紀念的大日子，擁有近50年歷史、作為日本最具人氣動漫角色之一的多啦A夢，正是其生日的大日子（漫畫設定於2112年9月3日誕生）！想在如此日子來趟相關旅程的話，作為《多》生父藤子．F．不二雄的故鄉富山縣高岡市，可謂最適合不過！市內遍布各式各樣以《多》為主題的有趣風景，當地更設有高岡市藤子．F．不二雄故鄉畫廊，內裏有難得一見的《多》系展品，教粉絲感受被多啦A夢大包圍的興奮。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_02p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_02p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=91d2bfc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n畫廊尋找多啦A夢<br />\n作為《多啦A夢》之旅的第一站，於2015年開設的高岡市藤子．F．不二雄故鄉畫廊絕對是值得率先前往。其入口處已採用了《多》的隨意門設計，亦有1：1的多啦A夢Figure來迎賓。館內劃分為多個展區，除了透過幻燈片形式展示了這位大師年少時的照片，及將14歲時親手繪製的冊子《妖怪島》由頭到尾展示外，亦有展出這位大師愛用的物件如扁平帽子及鋼筆等。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_03p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_03p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=10f7dae5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_08p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_08p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=9ae44f73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n作為藤子成長的地方，高岡市可說給了藤子不少創作養分，館內特別設有一個區域介紹《多啦A夢》中看到的高岡市風景，可看得出他對故鄉的情意結。另外定期更換主題及內容的企劃展示室，除了有難得一見的展示內容外，亦特別將椅子設計成《多》中經常出現的缸管，感覺十分親切。當地的傳統工藝品「高岡銅器」享負盛名，館內亦特別以該手藝炮製了一個多啦A夢銅像，採用了最初期漫畫的造型，感覺維妙維肖之餘，大家當然要跟其打卡留念喇！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_16p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_16p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=5d5fb193&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對銅像意猶未盡的話，高岡站內的交通廣場等候室亦有一個同樣以「高岡銅器」技術製作的高岡市多啦A夢郵筒，該設施是為了慶祝藤子80歲生忌而設置；而步出高岡站僅1分鐘腳程，就有條多啦A夢散步步道，大雄、靜香及多啦美等主要角色統統化身為銅像列陣，也真的夠壯觀呢。<br />\n<img src=\"http://puui.qpic.cn/qqvideo_ori/0/w0357xdu1sw_496_280/0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpuui.qpic.cn%2Fqqvideo_ori%2F0%2Fw0357xdu1sw_496_280%2F0&h=d31b6708&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高岡市藤子．F．不二雄故鄉畫廊<br />\n地址：富山縣高岡市中川1-1-30高岡市美術館2F<br />\n開放時間：9:30am~5:00pm（逢周一休館）<br />\n票價：成人￥500（約HK$35.5）<br />\n網址：<a href=\"http://fujiko-artgallery.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffujiko-artgallery.jp%2F&d=wqF2iYvzm1E%2BmilzLiuNgm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=a921a7ac\" target=\"_blank\">http://fujiko-artgallery.jp/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_11p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_11p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=6c4786e4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高岡市多啦A夢郵筒<br />\n地點：高岡站交通廣場（等候室）<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_09p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_09p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=1bc12a54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多啦A夢的散步道<br />\n地址：富山縣高岡市末廣町1-8"},{"pid":"809b07b0164179c1253285b33ed294d3f72fc074","tid":385650,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:33:22.000Z","msg":"重現經典空地<br />\n記得5年前「多啦A夢誕生前100年祭」在世界各地都有不同的慶祝搞作，而高岡市則為往來高岡市與射水市之間的萬葉線路面電車，推出特別版的多啦A夢電車。只見電車由外到內都充滿多啦A夢氣息，車身外觀塗上多啦A夢的招牌藍色，門口則繪上隨意門的粉紅色，加上車頭及車身玻璃都印有靜香、小夫等角色的線畫，可謂搶眼非常。同樣以藍色為主調的內籠，頂部印有多個角色的畫像外，更有不少搞鬼細節位，如1比1的多啦A夢剪影，各種法寶的圖案，讓大小朋友在車程中慢慢發掘。想乘搭的話，不妨先上網址Check一下當天列車行駛時間，免卻等車麻煩。<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_17p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_17p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=dc7ad4b4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另一個不可錯過的多啦A夢好去處，則是新高岡站附近的高岡御伽森林公園，內裏特別重現了《多》中大雄跟一班朋友放學後經常流連的空地，場內有一班神態和動作相當傳神的雕像之外，就連就招牌的缸管也忠實呈現出來。而離空地不遠處，則有一個多啦A夢主題日晷，上面附有縮小電筒、竹蜻蜓等法寶的浮雕，相當有意思！<br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_15p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_15p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=054118bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n高岡御伽森林公園<br />\n地址：富山縣高岡市佐野1342<br />\n開放時間：9:00am~5:00pm（逢周二休息）<br />\n網址：<a href=\"http://terfel.net/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fterfel.net%2F&d=wqF2iYvzm1E%2BmilzLiuNgm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f94a4a9c\" target=\"_blank\">http://terfel.net/</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/photo/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_13p.jpg?20170902170631\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001_13p.jpg%3F20170902170631&h=b57c4aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n多啦A夢列車<br />\n行程：高岡市高岡站往返射水市越潟站<br />\n票價：￥150（約HK$10.7）起<br />\n網址：<a href=\"http://www.manyosen.co.jp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.manyosen.co.jp%2F&d=wqF2iYvzm1E%2BmilzLiuNgm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=d5e3f837\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.manyosen.co.jp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Flifestyle%2F20170902%2Fbkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001.html&d=wqF2iYvzm1E%2BmilzLiuNgm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=f0e8452c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/lifestyle/20170902/bkn-20170902164313395-0902_00982_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"02d0ee3cbf9f8078ffc257d0dd297f60efc89295","tid":385650,"uid":56700,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:47:52.000Z","msg":"屌你個和坤做乜嘢衝出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d94d52da07d94ad2066c43be18efa5466bc2b71a","tid":385650,"uid":46911,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:51:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>屌你個和坤做乜嘢衝出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n：喂老紀"},{"pid":"b790d43913947dc9402eddab4ca826b4c3ad6698","tid":385650,"uid":60785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b71b2a579615e357fa8a49a0a323df8d8efcc420","tid":385650,"uid":4180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T12:35:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>屌你個和坤做乜嘢衝出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n：喂老紀</blockquote><br />\n夠薑就一針打撚死我<br />\n阿叔我嚇大既<br />\n屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SyoJdx0w9B4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DSyoJdx0w9B4&d=wqF2iYvzm1E%2BmilzLiuNgm6kGZraZVKwHE52VSkiKoI%3D&h=490f8a80\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=SyoJdx0w9B4</a>"},{"pid":"d837d053c0b66861650327a6db0c612a95a16bac","tid":385650,"uid":3698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T12:44:33.000Z","msg":"櫈登櫈登： 鐵齒銅牙紀曉嵐～～"},{"pid":"95404ec468acbc6379b149f649f17f6de669a1b8","tid":385650,"uid":127583,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-03T13:00:04.000Z","msg":"好掛全保全叔把聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}